---
title: Beef Rump & Bacon Filo Pie with Mushrooms, Thyme & Parmesan
description: If you’ve been craving a good pie, don’t worry so have we but let’s not settle for any old one. You can still get those luxurious dining vibes whilst satisfying your tastebuds latest obsession. Tender beef steak, cooked with bacon and mushrooms is enough to elevate any dish, but with the aromatic scent of thyme, this pie hits five stars!
